---
---
<section class="bg-primary-50 dark:bg-primary-950 transition-colors duration-300 py-28 sm:py-36">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-10">

    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 w-full max-w-xs">
      <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-primary-200 dark:bg-primary-800"></div>
      <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rotate-45 bg-primary-300 dark:bg-primary-700 flex-shrink-0"></div>
      <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-primary-200 dark:bg-primary-800"></div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-light italic text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 leading-snug"
       style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;">
      Frå Ryfylke-fjorden til flaska di — med stoltheit gjennom generasjonar.
    </p>

    <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-primary-400 dark:text-primary-600">
      Fuglestein Fruktgard · Jelsa, Norge
    </span>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center pt-2">
      <a href="/product"
         class="px-8 py-3.5 text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase bg-primary-900 dark:bg-primary-100 text-primary-50 dark:text-primary-900 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity duration-200">
        Besøk nettbutikken
      </a>
      <a href="/contact"
         class="px-8 py-3.5 text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase border border-primary-200 dark:border-primary-800 text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 hover:bg-primary-100 dark:hover:bg-primary-900 transition-colors duration-200">
        Ta kontakt
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 w-full max-w-xs">
      <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-primary-200 dark:bg-primary-800"></div>
      <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rotate-45 bg-primary-300 dark:bg-primary-700 flex-shrink-0"></div>
      <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-primary-200 dark:bg-primary-800"></div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>